OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784751304
OL,3,CMaternity review to examine thousands
OL,4,Cof cases of mothers and babies
OL,6,FOn Saturday, 18 July midwife Donna
OL,7,FOckenden, who is to lead the review
OL,8,Finto maternity and neonatal services
OL,9,Fat Leeds General Infirmary and St
OL,10,FJames's Hospital, met scores of
OL,11,Fmothers and bereaved families who say
OL,12,Fthey were failed by the trust.
OL,14,FThe review is yet to begin in earnest,
OL,15,Fbut according to Ms Ockenden, today's
OL,16,Fmeeting in Leeds was vital to help
OL,17,Fshape its terms of reference and put
OL,18,Ffamilies at the heart of its work.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784751304
OL,3,CMaternity review to examine thousands
OL,4,Cof cases of mothers and babies
OL,6,FMs Ockenden said: "At the end of this
OL,7,Fentire process I think two things.
OL,8,FFirstly; that families will receive
OL,9,Fthe answers that they've been looking
OL,10,Ffor, searching for, sometimes ,for
OL,11,Fmany years.
OL,13,F"Secondly; maternity improvements both
OL,14,Flocally here in Leeds and across
OL,15,FEngland."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
