PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784751304
OL,3,CMaternity review to examine thousands
OL,4,Cof cases of mothers and babies
OL,6,FThe review is expected to examine
OL,7,Fcases of stillbirths, neonatal deaths
OL,8,Fand serious incidents, hypoxic
OL,9,Finjuries and maternal deaths over a 15-
OL,10,Fyear period from 1 Jan 2011 to 31 Dec
OL,11,F2025.
OL,13,FFiona Winser-Ramm and Daniel Ramm
OL,14,Fwhose daughter Aliona died just 27
OL,15,Fminutes after she was born in 2020,
OL,16,Fmet with Donna Ockenden today.
OL,18,FAn inquest found that there had been
OL,19,F"a number of gross failures of the
OL,20,Fmost basic nature that directly
OL,21,Fcontributed to Aliona's death."
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
