FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784751304
OL,3,CMaternity review to examine thousands
OL,4,Cof cases of mothers and babies
OL,6,FFiona said: "This is now really just
OL,7,Fthe beginning of actually beginning to
OL,8,Fexamine everything and look for the
OL,9,Fanswers and accountability that
OL,10,Ffamilies deserve."
OL,12,FDaniel said:" It's been pretty
OL,13,Fapparent certainly since our daughter
OL,14,Fdied that there have been a large
OL,15,Fnumber of systemic problems at Leeds
OL,16,FTeaching Hospitals Trust and the care
OL,17,Fthat they provide that have been
OL,18,Fongoing for some time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784751304
OL,3,CMaternity review to examine thousands
OL,4,Cof cases of mothers and babies
OL,6,F"The importance of this inquiry is to
OL,7,Fallow families to get answers to
OL,8,Fwhat's happened to them, their cases
OL,9,Fand for them to seek accountability
OL,10,Ffor what's happened to their babies
OL,11,Fand what's happened to birthing people
OL,12,Fas well."
OL,14,FBrendan Brown, Chief Executive of
OL,15,FLeeds Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I am deeply sorry to families
OL,17,Fwhose babies have sadly died or who
OL,18,Fhave been harmed when receiving care
OL,19,Fin our hospitals.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1784751304
OL,3,CMaternity review to examine thousands
OL,4,Cof cases of mothers and babies
OL,6,F"I know apologies are not enough, and
OL,7,Fwe are absolutely committed to working
OL,8,Fopenly, honestly and transparently
OL,9,Fwith Donna Ockenden and the review
OL,10,Fteam, and with families who have used
OL,11,Four services. We hope this review will
OL,12,Fprovide families with the answers they
OL,13,Fdeserve.
OL,15,F"Significant improvements are already
OL,16,Funderway in our maternity and neonatal
OL,17,Fservices; we know there is much more
OL,18,Fto do and we are committed to improve
OL,19,Fand ensure that every family receives
OL,20,Fsafe, compassionate, inclusive, and
OL,21,Fhigh-quality care."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU}D@SO]
